songs.title: Impossible (Cover)
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1: Normani]
I remember years ago, someone told me I should take
Caution when it comes to love, I did, I did
And you were strong and I was not, my illusion, my mistake
I was careless, I forgot, I did

[Pre-Chorus: Lauren]
And now, all is done, there is nothing to say
You have gone and so effortlessly
You have won, you can go ahead
Tell them

[Chorus: Lauren & Ally & Normani and Dinah]
Tell them all I know now, shout it from the rooftops
Write it on the skyline, all we had is gone now
Tell them I was happy and my heart is broken
All my scars are open, tell them what I hoped would be
Impossible
Impossible
Impossible
Impossible

[Bridge: Camila]
I remember years ago, someone told me I should take
Caution when it comes to love, I did

[Chorus: Camila & Dinah & All]
Tell them all I know now, shout it from the rooftops
Write it on the skyline, all we had is gone now
Tell them I was happy and my heart is broken
All my scars are open, tell them what I hoped would be
Impossible
Impossible
Impossible
Impossible
Impossible

[Outro: All]
Impossible
Impossible
Impossible
Impossible
